      "solution": "<p><strong>Correct Answer: B)</strong> 2, 3, 5</p>\n\n<p><strong>Explanation : </strong></p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:693px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:bottom\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Characteristic</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:bottom\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Squamous Cell <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"988c19e3131692777183b6744d1920\">Carcinoma</span> (SCC)</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:bottom\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Adenocarcinoma of Esophagus</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Predominant location</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Upper two-thirds</strong> of the oesophagus <strong><strong>(Statement 1 ruled out)</strong></strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p>The lower third of the oesophagus, near GE junction</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Epidemiology</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p>Overall, the<strong> more common type<strong> (Statement 4 ruled out)</strong></strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p>Increasing due to an increase in GERD</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Risk Factors</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Smoking, Alcohol</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>HPV infection</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Caustic <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"192677035a169277718780b4d6dbbb\">esophageal</span> injury,</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Achalasia</strong></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Tylosis</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Plummer-Vinson syndrome</strong></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Diets deficient in fruits or vegetables</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Frequent consumption of very</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\n\t\t\t<p>Hot beverages.</p>\n\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Previous <strong>radiation</strong> to the mediastinum</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Fermented milk (mursik) containing acetaldehyde</strong></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Chronic <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"9f47bfb9a616927771887db45c89c7\">gastroesophageal</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"def94cc96d16927771970d1a5cfb71\">reflux</span> disease (GERD)</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Obesity</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Smoking</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Low fruit and vegetable diet</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Scleroderma</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>p16 and RB gene mutations</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Protective factor</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p>Healthy diet</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p>H.pylori- reduces acid, hence reducing GERD.</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Precursor Lesion</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p>None</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p>Barrett's <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"84f4cb0ade16927771940b83eacc37\">oesophagus</span> (metaplasia of <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"5be0ee4ea316927771997104326685\">squamous</span> to columnar)</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Histology</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p>Keratinisation and <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"0707c047ba1692777195ce682d9eca\">pearl</span> formation</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><img alt=\"Squamous cell carcinoma esophagus\" data-author=\"Mikael Haggstrom\" data-hash=\"734\" data-license=\"CC0 1.0\" data-source=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Histopathology_of_squamous-cell_carcinoma.png\" data-tags=\"January2025\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/notes/5Mb90i4lgBnNAveplnQA1736867561.png\" /></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p>Glandular differentiation</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><img alt=\"Adenocarcinoma esophagus\" data-author=\"Mikael Haggstrom\" data-hash=\"735\" data-license=\"CC0 1.0\" data-source=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Histopathology_of_adenocarcinoma.png\" data-tags=\"January2025\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/notes/Jy1BCWp0LWHGzG0OesX91736867637.jpg\" /></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Clinical Presentation</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p>Dysphagia, weight loss, chest pain</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p>Dysphagia, GERD symptoms, weight loss</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Prognosis</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p>Generally less favourable</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-left:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-right:1px solid #0d0d0d; border-top:1px solid #0d0d0d; vertical-align:middle\">\n\t\t\t<p>Generally more favourable</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p> </p>",
